name: GE Under Cabinet LED Light Fixture
description: Light your counters with the GE 18 in. Direct Wire under cabinet LED fixture. This high powered fixture mounts under any cabinet, bathing your task area in a bright warm light suitable for any task, and can be switched to a low level for accent lighting/nightlight.
